<P><font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="5"><b>Letters to the editor</b></font></p>
<p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">July 20, 2001 | Page 4</font></p>

<p><font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="3">OTHER LETTERS BELOW<br>
<a href="#Sinking">The tragic sinking of a sweatshop at sea</a><br>
<a href="#Papua">Papua New Guinea cops gun down protesters</a><br>
